document_data.mainbody: '''Starlings''' were a species of common [[bird]] found in several habitats in [[Faerûn]], including the [[Sword Coast North]], [[Interior Faerûn]], and the [[Vilhon Reach]].
document_data.Description: Starling were small diurnal birds that flew in noisy swirling flocks.
document_data.Ecology: Starlings could be found inhabiting the [[Blade Kingdoms]] of the Vilhon Reach, nesting within the city of [[Sumbria]] and swirling above the [[Palace of Manniccis]]. and nesting in the [[Hulorn]]'s statuaries. In the [[Land of the Lions]], starlings and [[jay]]s eagerly controlled the insect population during the day.
